DOC.brief_summary: The study evaluates treatment procedure, efficacy and safety of NASHA BE for female breast enhancement.
DOC.brief_title: NASHA BE for Enhancement of the Shape and Fullness of the Female Breast
DOC.criteria: Female between 25 and 50 years of age with small breasts seeking enhancement of the shape and fullness of the breast Unreasonable expectations Any medical condition that may interfere with the treatment
